name: WAGMI GAMES from Ethereum
description: Bridged from Ethereum via https://bridge.pulsechain.com. Original Address - 0x3B604747ad1720C01ded0455728b62c0d2F100F0. WAGMI Defense is being developed as the Clash Royale of crypto with a futuristic twist. This epic aliens versus humans game is being built on unity as a browser based, mobile responsive game with plans to launch on IOS and Apple Store when it becomes crypto accepted.
